NAME
    Template::Plugin::Octets - Format numeric values as binary octets

VERSION
    version 0.15

SYNOPSIS
        [% USE Octets -%]
        [% Octets.mio(bytes_recv) %]

METHODS
    kio Format value to kibioctets (2^10 octets).

    mio Format value to mebioctets (2^20 octets).

    gio Format value to gibioctets (2^30 octets).

SEE ALSO
    Template

    Template::Plugin::Procedural

